channel.title: Whats a good source?
channel.description:
i want a good source that is dependable, i am a good coder, my dad has a life in coding, so he can help me with some errors etc, but thats not the point, i want a great stable server, that i, myself, can get some java experience and have a fun time doing, my goal is looking at the server when its first made (right after i download it) and than changing the area to a whole new location, ive done it once with pimpscape, but when i tried to make the wild area nonwild, i discovered the server is junk, meaning the server had tons of errors, and it wasn't my code, it was the server itself. so anyway, i am posting this so i can understand what a good source is so i don't waste my time again, please help guys, i am looking forward to starting ASAP, thanks so much ~flargie~
~~~+flargie+~~~~
